\c 10
\s Indlovukazi yeShebha
\p
\v 1 Kwathi indlovukazi\x + 2 Lan. 9.1-12. Mat. 12.42. Luka 11.31.\x* yeShebha\x + Gen. 10.28. 25.3. 1 Lan. 1.32. Jobe 1.15. 6.19. Hlab. 72.10,15. Isa. 60.6. Jer. 6.20. Hez. 27.22,23. 38.13. Jow. 3.8.\x* isizwile udumo lukaSolomoni ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd* yeza ukumhlola ngemibuzo enzima\x + Hlu. 14.12.\x*.
\v 2 Yasifika eJerusalema lodwendwe olukhulu kakhulu, lamakamela ethwele amakha legolide elinengi kakhulu lamatshe aligugu; isifikile kuSolomoni yamtshela konke okwakusenhliziyweni yayo.
\v 3 USolomoni waseyichasisela zonke indaba zayo; kwakungelalutho olwayicatshelayo inkosi engayichasiselanga lona.
\v 4 Indlovukazi yeShebha isibonile yonke inhlakanipho kaSolomoni, lendlu ayeyakhile,
\v 5 lokudla kwetafula lakhe, lokuhlala kwezinceku zakhe, lokuma kwezisebenzi zakhe, lezigqoko zazo, labaphathinkezo bakhe, lokwenyuka kwakhe enyuka ngakho endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Lan. 26.16. 2 Lan. 9.4. Hez. 40.26.\x*, kakusabanga lamoya kuyo\x + Josh. 5.1.\x*.
\v 6 Yasisithi enkosini: Umbiko wawuliqiniso engawuzwa elizweni lami ngamazwi akho langenhlakanipho yakho.
\v 7 Kodwa kangiyikholwanga leyomibiko ngaze ngafika lamehlo ami abona. Khangela, bengingatshelwanga ingxenye; wengezelele inhlakanipho lokulunga embikweni engiwuzwileyo.
\v 8 Bayathokoza abantu bakho, ziyathokoza lezizinceku zakho ezimi njalo phambi kwakho zisizwa inhlakanipho yakho\x + Zaga 8.34.\x*!
\v 9 Kayibusiswe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyathokoza ngawe, ukukubeka phezu kwesihlalo sobukhosi sikaIsrayeli\x + 5.7.\x*. Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yamthanda uIsrayeli kuze kube phakade\x + 2 Lan. 2.11.\x*, ngakho ikubekile waba yinkosi ukuze wenze isahlulelo lokulunga\x + 2 Sam. 8.15. Hlab. 72.2.\x*.
\v 10 Yasinika inkosi \w amathalenta\w** alikhulu lamatshumi amabili egolide, lamakha amanengi kakhulu, lamatshe aligugu. Kakuzange kusabuya amakha ngobunengi njengalawo indlovukazi yeShebha eyawanika inkosi uSolomoni\x + 10.2. Hlab. 72.10,15.\x*.
\v 11 Futhi lemikhumbi kaHiramu\x + 9.27.\x* eyayithwala igolide livela eOfiri\x + 9.28.\x* yaletha izigodo ezinengi kakhulu zomkampa, lamatshe aligugu, kuvela eOfiri.
\v 12 Ngezigodo zomkampa inkosi yasisenza insika zendlu kaJehova lezendlu yenkosi, lamachacho lezigubhu zezintambo kwabahlabeleli; kakuzanga kulethwe kumbe kubonwe ngokunjalo izigodo zomkampa kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 13 Inkosi uSolomoni yasinika indlovukazi yeShebha sonke isiloyiso sayo, eyakucelayo, ngaphandle kwalokho eyayinika khona njengokuphana kwenkosi uSolomoni. Yasiphenduka yaya elizweni layo, yona lenceku zayo.
\s Inotho kaSolomoni lodumo lwakhe
\p
\v 14 Njalo isisindo segolide elalifika kuSolomoni ngomnyaka owodwa \w sasingamathalenta\w** angamakhulu ayisithupha lamatshumi ayisithupha lesithupha\x + 1 Lan. 9.13-28.\x*,
\v 15 ngaphandle kokuvela kubathengisi, lempahleni zabathengisi bezinongo, lemakhosini wonke eArabhiya, lakubabusi belizwe\x + Neh. 3.31,32. 13.20. Hez. 17.4. 27.3. Nah. 3.16.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Inkosi uSolomoni yasisenza izihlangu ezinkulu ezingamakhulu amabili ngegolide elikhandiweyo, \add amashekeli\add* angamakhulu ayisithupha egolide esihlangwini esisodwa esikhulu.
\v 17 Lamahawu angamakhulu amathathu egolide elikhandiweyo\x + 14.26.\x*; \w amamane\w** amathathu egolide ehawini elilodwa\x + 2 Lan. 9.16.\x*. Inkosi yasiwafaka endlini yegusu leLebhanoni\x + 10.21. 7.2.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Inkosi yenza lesihlalo sobukhosi esikhulu ngempondo zendlovu, yasihuqa ngegolide elicwengekileyo\x + 2 Lan. 9.17.\x*.
\v 19 Isihlalo sobukhosi sasilezikhwelo eziyisithupha, lesihloko sesihlalo sobukhosi sasiyisigombolozi emuva, lezeyamelo zengalo ngapha langapha kuze kube sendaweni yokuhlala, lezilwane ezimbili zimi eceleni kwezeyamelo zezingalo.
\v 20 Lezilwane ezilitshumi lambili zazimi lapho ezikhwelweni eziyisithupha, ngapha langapha. Kakwenziwanga okunjalo kuwo wonke umbuso.
\p
\v 21 Lazo zonke inkezo zokunatha zenkosi uSolomoni zazingezegolide, lazo zonke izitsha zendlu yegusu leLebhanoni zazingezegolide elicwengekileyo; kwakungelasiliva, lalingabalwa santo ensukwini zikaSolomoni\x + 10.17.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba inkosi yayilemikhumbi yeThashishi olwandle kanye lemikhumbi kaHiramu; kanye ngeminyaka emithathu limikhumbi yeThashishi yeza ithwele igolide lesiliva\x + 22.48. Gen. 10.4. 1 Lan. 1.7. 2 Lan. 20.36,37. Hlab. 48.7. 72.10. Isa. 2.16. 23.1,6,10,14. 60.9. 66.19. Jer. 10.9. Hez. 27.12,25. 38.13. Jona 1.3. 4.2.\x*, impondo zezindlovu lezinkawu lamaphigaga.
\v 23 Ngakho inkosi uSolomoni yaba nkulu kulawo wonke amakhosi omhlaba enothweni lenhlakanipheni\x + 3.12,13. 4.30. 2 Lan. 1.12.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Umhlaba wonke wasudinga ubuso bukaSolomoni ukuzwa inhlakanipho yakhe uNkulunkulu ayeyinike enhliziyweni yakhe.
\v 25 Basebeletha, ngulowo isipho sakhe, izitsha zesiliva, lezitsha zegolide, lezembatho, lezikhali, lamakha, amabhiza, lezimbongolo; into yomnyaka ngomnyaka wayo\x + 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*.
\p
\v 26 USolomoni wasebuthanisa izinqola labagadi bamabhiza\x + 2 Lan. 1.14-17.\x*; wayelezinqola ezingamakhulu alitshumi lane, labagadi bamabhiza abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili; wakubeka emizini yezinqola njalo kulenkosi eJerusalema\x + 4.26. 2 Lan. 1.14. 9.25.\x*.
\v 27 Inkosi yasisenza isiliva eJerusalema laba njengamatshe\x + 2 Lan. 9.27. Jobe 22.24.\x*, lemisedari wayenza yaba njengemikhiwa yesikhamore esesihotsheni, ngobunengi\x + 1 Lan. 27.28.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Wasengenisa ngokuthenga amabhiza avela eGibhithe, ayengekaSolomoni, lelembu elicolekileyo; labathengi benkosi babelithatha ilembu elicolekileyo ngentengo\x + 2 Lan. 9.28. Dute. 17.16.\x*.
\v 29 Inqola yasisenyuka yaphuma eGibhithe nga\add mashekeli\add* esiliva angamakhulu ayisithupha, lebhiza ngekhulu lamatshumi amahlanu. Langokunjalo ba\add wa\add*khuphela wonke amakhosi amaHethi lamakhosi eSiriya ngesandla sabo\x + 11.1. Hlu. 1.26.\x*.